    <p>JENNA(ph): I'm Jenna. </p>
    <p>MOLLY: Right here at CES 2007, launching a new product. It's little </p>
    <p>HANSEN: Victor Godinez is the technology reporter for the Dallas Morning News. He came to us by way of member station KERA. </p>
