    <p>Mr. MITT ROMNEY (Former Republican Governor, Massachusetts; Presidential Candidate): Well, another silver, and it's - I'd rather have a gold, but I got another silver. And now there've been... </p>
    <p>(Soundbite of cheering crowd) </p>
