    <p>Ms. BROWNWOOD: I did. I saw that replayed on the news and... </p>
    <p>WERTHEIMER: What did it look like to you? </p>
    <p>Ms. BROWNWOOD: It looked like that she was truly moved. And earlier, someone had said to me, knowing that I was a Hillary supporter, that she had no soul, and I think she proved that she indeed had soul. </p>
