    <p>Mr. GIBBS: This job and the only way I know to do it is you're going after it night and day. And I think the thrill of it is just that - it's how hard it is. My family situation being what it is right now, I just - I did not feel like I could make the kind of commitment that I need to make going forward this year. I felt like that they needed me. </p>
