    <p>Ms. ETHYL MERMAN (Singer) Boy, you've got the equipment. </p>
    <p>Mr. DURANTE: What do you mean? What do you mean? </p>
    <p>Ms. MERMAN: (Singing) I mean that if I catch a little cold... </p>
    <p>Mr. DURANTE: (Singing) I'll sneeze for you. </p>
    <p>Ms. MERMAN: (Singing) ...on a frosty winter day. </p>
