    <p>(Soundbite of speech) </p>
    <p>Sen. OBAMA: The same message we had when we were up and when we were down </p>
    <p>(Soundbite of cheering) </p>
    <p>Sen. OBAMA: that out of many, we are one; that while we breathe, we will hope; and where we are met with cynicism, and doubt, and fear, and those who tell us that we can't, we will respond with that timeless creed that sums up the spirit of the American people in three simple words: Yes, we can. </p>
